---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="About | Dinithi Studio"
			description="Learn more about Dinithi Studio and the creative strategy, SEO content, and web copy services behind the work."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.5rem;">
			<h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">About</h1>
			<p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
				I’m Dinithi Jayasekara, a creative strategist focused on SEO content, website copy, and content planning for brands that want to sound clearer and grow with intention.
			</p>
			<p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
				My work sits at the intersection of messaging, search behaviour, and structure. I help brands create content that feels human, commercially aware, and easier to navigate.
			</p>
			<p style="line-height: 1.8;">
				I’ve worked across industries including legal, digital marketing, trades, finance, jewellery, and tourism.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>